OL,3,CBody Shop set to close almost half of
OL,4,Cits stores
OL,6,Fwill close almost half of its stores,
OL,7,Fwith seven set to shut on Tuesday, the
OL,8,Fcompany's administrators have
OL,9,Fannounced.
OL,11,FThe store has roughly 200 outlets
OL,12,Facross the UK, with over 2,000 staff
OL,13,Ffearing for their jobs, and went into
OL,14,Fadministration last week.
OL,16,FIt will also cut around 270 head
OL,17,Foffice jobs as part of a heavy
OL,18,Frestructuring.
