OL,3,CBody Shop set to close almost half of
OL,4,Cits stores
OL,6,FIt comes just weeks after private
OL,7,Fequity firm Aurelius took over the
OL,8,Fbusiness after buying The Body Shop
OL,9,Ffor #207 million in November.
OL,11,FA source close to Aurelius told ITV
OL,12,FNews that The Body Shop sits in a "far
OL,13,Fworse financial state" than it had
OL,14,Fanticipated when it acquired the brand.
OL,16,FThe retailer was founded in 1976 by
OL,17,FAnita Roddick and her husband Gordon
OL,18,Fas one of the first companies to
OL,19,Fpromote so-called ethical consumerism,
OL,20,Ffocusing on ethically produced
OL,21,Fcosmetics and skincare products.
